{"word":"G2664 - καταπαύω - katapaúō - kat-ap-ow'-o - Cease","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταπαύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katapaúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ap-ow'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cease</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அமர்த்து, இளைப்பாறு, ஓய்ந்திரு"},{"paragraph":"1. transitive, to make quiet, to cause to be at rest, to grant rest"},{"paragraph":"2. to rest, take rest"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G3973 - παύω - paúō - pow'-o/3973\">G3973</a>; to <i>settle down</i>, that is, (literally) to <i>colonize</i>, or (figuratively) to (<i>cause to</i>) <i>desist:</i> - cease, (give) rest (-rain).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2663/2663\">G2663</a>, <a href=\"#/G2664/2664\">G2664</a>"}]}